    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>摘要： <span id="more"></span></p><br><ul><li><p>点击tab可以自动补全一些东西，比如命令、文件名</p></li><li><p>关机</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">poweroff</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装deb文件</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg -<span class="selector-tag">i</span> 你的deb包名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>强制删除文件</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rm</span> <span class="operator">-f</span> 文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>强制删除文件夹</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf 文件夹名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>新建文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> 文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>建立文件夹</p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir 文件夹名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
